BaseCollectionReader, CollectionReader, ConfigurableResource, Resource
public class PropbankGoldReader
extends CollectionReader_ImplBase


Copyright (c) 2007-2008, Regents of the University of Colorado
All rights reserved.

Author:
Philip Ogren

PropbankCollectionReader reads all .mrg files of the WSJ part of Treebank in lexical order, then reads the corresponding Propbank entries, and populates the "TreebankView" and "PropbankView" SOFAs.

, Philip Ogren, Philipp Wetzler

Field Detail

PARAM_PROPBANK_CORPUS_FILE

public static final String PARAM_PROPBANK_CORPUS_FILE
The descriptor file should have a parameter called 'PropbankCorpusFile' that points to propbank data (e.g. propbank-1.0/props.txt).

See Also:
Constant Field Values

PARAM_TREEBANK_CORPUS_DIRECTORY

public static final String PARAM_TREEBANK_CORPUS_DIRECTORY
The top level directory of Treebank. There must be a directory wsj under this, which contains subdirectories for the sections.

See Also:
Constant Field Values

PARAM_WSJ_SECTIONS

public static final String PARAM_WSJ_SECTIONS
This determines which sections of WSJ will be used. The format allows for comma-separated section numbers and section ranges, for example "02,07-12,16".
